import React, { useState } from 'react'; const FATCAUpload = ({ onSubmit, loading }) => { const [formData, setFormData] = useState({ reg_details: [{ pan_rp: '', pekrn: '', inv_name: '', dob: '', fr_name: '', sp_name: '', tax_status: '04', data_src: 'P', addr_type: '3', po_bir_inc: '', co_bir_inc: 'IN', tax_res1: 'IN', tpin1: '', id1_type: 'C', tax_res2: '', tpin2: '', id2_type: '', tax_res3: '', tpin3: '', id3_type: '', tax_res4: '', tpin4: '', id4_type: '', srce_wealt: '02', corp_servs: '01', inc_slab: '32', net_worth: '', nw_date: '', pep_flag: 'N', occ_code: '01', occ_type: 'B', exemp_code: 'M', ffi_drnfe: 'FFI', giin_no: '', spr_entity: '', giin_na: 'NO', giin_exemc: '1', nffe_catg: 'A', act_nfe_sc: '07', nature_bus: '', rel_listed: '', exch_name: 'O', ubo_appl: 'Y', ubo_count: '1', sdf_flag: 'Y', ubo_df: 'Y', aadhaar_rp: '', new_change: '', log_name: '', ubo_exch: 'B', ubo_isin: '', ubo_rel_li: '', npo_form: 'N', npo_dcl: '', npo_rgno: '', ubo_details: [] }] }); const handleChange = (e) => { const { name, value } = e.target; setFormData(prev => ({ reg_details: [{ ...prev.reg_details[0], [name]: value }] })); }; const formatDate = (dateString) => { if (!dateString) return ''; const date = new Date(dateString); const day = date.getDate().toString().padStart(2, '0'); const month = (date.getMonth() + 1).toString().padStart(2, '0'); const year = date.getFullYear(); return `${day}/${month}/${year}`; }; const handleSubmit = (e) => { e.preventDefault(); // Format dates const formattedData = { reg_details: [{ ...formData.reg_details[0], dob: formatDate(formData.reg_details[0].dob), nw_date: formatDate(formData.reg_details[0].nw_date) }] }; onSubmit(formattedData); }; return (
FATCA Registration
); }; export default FATCAUpload;
